Getting started

1. Clone the style guide

Before you start a project, make sure you clone the Relume Library Style Guide on Webflow.

Clone now

2. Copy component

Search through the Relume Library to find components and copy them with 1 click.

Browse all components

3. Paste in to project

Once a component is copied to your clipboard, simply paste it into your Webflow project.

Create Webflow project
